### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health
Accept: application/json

### Initialize Interview Session
# @name init_session
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/interview/initialize
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "role": "Backend Engineer",
    "level": "senior",
    "skills": ["python", "mongodb", "system_design"],
    "user_email": "candidate@example.com",
    "questions_per_skill": 2
}

###

# Save the session ID from the previous request
@session_id = {{init_session.response.body.session_id}}

### WebSocket Streaming
# Note: Standard HTTP REST clients cannot execute WebSocket connections.
# Use Postman's WebSocket tool and connect to:
# ws://localhost:8000/api/v1/interview/stream/{{session_id}}


### Finalize Interview (Trigger Background Report)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/interview/{{session_id}}/finalize
Accept: application/json


### Get Interview Report
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/interview/{{session_id}}/report
Accept: application/json
